<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 12:10:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>教宗为海地和平祈祷</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/pope-offers-prayers-calls-for-peace-in-haiti/articleshow/108369135.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108369135.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;教宗方济各在最近犯罪团伙造成的动乱中为海地祈祷。他为结束暴力祈祷，呼吁各方“在国际社会的重新支持下”努力实现和平与和解。犯罪团伙已经控制了首都太子港的大部分地区以及通往该国其他地区的道路。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 11:43:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/pope-offers-prayers-calls-for-peace-in-haiti/articleshow/108369135.cms</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫从土耳其购买无人机用于巡逻该国广阔的海域</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/maldives-purchases-drones-from-turkey-to-patrol-countrys-vast-maritime-area/articleshow/108368464.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108368464.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马尔代夫首次从土耳其购买无人侦察机。在努努环礁马法鲁建立了无人机基地。穆罕默德·穆伊祖 (Mohamed Muizzu) 于 11 月访问土耳其，并达成了进口军用无人机的协议。无人机于3月3日交付。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 10:42:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/maldives-purchases-drones-from-turkey-to-patrol-countrys-vast-maritime-area/articleshow/108368464.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部称战争死亡人数为 31,045 人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/health-ministry-in-hamas-run-gaza-says-war-death-toll-at-31045/articleshow/108366880.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108366880.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部周日表示，在以色列和巴勒斯坦武装分子之间五个多月的战争中，该地区至少有 31,045 人死亡。外交部声明称，最新死亡人数包括过去 24 小时内 85 人死亡，并补充说，自 10 月 7 日战争开始以来，加沙已有 72,654 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/health-ministry-in-hamas-run-gaza-says-war-death-toll-at-31045/articleshow/108366880.cms</guid></item><item><title>基辅空军：乌克兰一夜之间击落35架俄罗斯无人机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/kyiv-air-force-ukraine-downed-35-russian-drones-overnight/articleshow/108366741.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108366741.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;基辅空军声称周日在包括首都地区在内的乌克兰各地击落了 35 架俄罗斯无人机。​​乌克兰空军表示，击落的无人机发生在中部地区以及南部地区，而导弹则击落了这架无人机。袭击针对东部地区，造成至少九人受伤。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:00:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/kyiv-air-force-ukraine-downed-35-russian-drones-overnight/articleshow/108366741.cms</guid></item><item><title>葡萄牙大选可能会加剧欧洲因腐败和困难而右倾的势头</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/portugals-election-could-add-momentum-to-europes-drift-to-the-right-due-to-corruption-hardship/articleshow/108367792.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108367792.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;葡萄牙大选因腐败丑闻、经济困难、住房危机和不满情绪而受到损害。随着激进右翼民粹主义政党获得支持，温和派政党可能会失去信心。切加可能成为拥王者。佩德罗·努诺·桑托斯和路易斯·黑山承诺做出改变。安德烈·文图拉在社交媒体上吸引年轻人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 10:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/portugals-election-could-add-momentum-to-europes-drift-to-the-right-due-to-corruption-hardship/articleshow/108367792.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列空袭消灭了杀害加沙军官的目标</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-airstrike-eliminates-target-who-killed-israeli-officer-in-gaza/articleshow/108367041.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108367041.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据周日发布的官方声明，以色列国防军（IDF）已成功消灭了杀害阿米沙尔·本·大卫少校（预备役）的恐怖分子。​​担任突击队旅长的本·大卫少校前锋指挥小组周五在加沙南部被杀。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:21:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-airstrike-eliminates-target-who-killed-israeli-officer-in-gaza/articleshow/108367041.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯妇女在乌克兰库尔斯克村炮击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-woman-killed-in-shelling-by-ukraine-in-kursk-village/articleshow/108366989.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108366989.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;库尔巴基村一名妇女因乌克兰炮击而丧生。她的丈夫受了重伤。俄罗斯对乌克兰的军事攻势已持续三年，在其南部地区摧毁了47架乌克兰无人机。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:58:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-woman-killed-in-shelling-by-ukraine-in-kursk-village/articleshow/108366989.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我不是年轻人，但是……”：拜登发布竞选广告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/i-am-not-a-young-guy-but-biden-releases-campaigning-ad/articleshow/108365987.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108365987.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乔·拜登发布了一个竞选广告，强调了他的政府的成就，并将自己与唐纳德·特朗普进行了对比。他谈到自己的年龄，说自己不年轻了。他强调了在 COVID-19 应对、经济和处方药成本方面取得的成就。拜登还提到了基础设施、气候变化、堕胎权以及选民对最高法院任命的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/i-am-not-a-young-guy-but-biden-releases-campaigning-ad/articleshow/108365987.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰炮击俄罗斯边境村庄 一名妇女丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/woman-killed-in-ukrainian-shelling-in-russian-border-village/articleshow/108366945.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108366945.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯库尔斯克州库尔巴基定居点因炮击引发火灾，一名妇女死亡，她的丈夫受伤。另一户人家遭到袭击。乌克兰指责俄罗斯对米尔诺格勒镇发动袭击，造成至少九人受伤，九座高层建筑受损。州长 Roman Starovoit 在他的 Telegram 频道上报道了这一事件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:29:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/woman-killed-in-ukrainian-shelling-in-russian-border-village/articleshow/108366945.cms</guid></item><item><title>波音747-9空中故障：无法找到门板维修记录</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/boeing-747-9-mid-air-malfunction-boeing-admit-inability-to-locate-records-for-door-panel-maintenance-alaska-airlines/articleshow/108366020.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108366020.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波音公司在给国会的一封信中承认，无法找到阿拉斯加航空航班飞行期间出现故障的门板的维护记录。参议员玛丽亚·坎特韦尔 (Maria Cantwell) 要求就阿拉斯加航空公司波音 737-9 机队停飞一事做出回应。阿拉斯加航空首席执行官本·米尼库奇宣布紧急迫降波特兰。有关华盛顿州伦顿面板拆除和重新安装的记录可能永远不会生成。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 08:17:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/boeing-747-9-mid-air-malfunction-boeing-admit-inability-to-locate-records-for-door-panel-maintenance-alaska-airlines/articleshow/108366020.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦载有炸药的摩托车发生爆炸，两人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/two-dead-after-motorcycle-loaded-with-explosives-blasts-in-pakistan/articleshow/108366555.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108366555.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一辆载有炸药的摩托车在巴基斯坦白沙瓦爆炸，造成两人死亡、一人受伤。摩托车上装有约4至5公斤炸药。当局尚未确认任何组织声称对爆炸负责。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 08:55:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/two-dead-after-motorcycle-loaded-with-explosives-blasts-in-pakistan/articleshow/108366555.cms</guid></item><item><title>葡萄牙大选投票开始，主流温和派试图阻止民粹主义者</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/polls-open-in-portugals-general-election-with-mainstream-moderates-trying-to-keep-populists-at-bay/articleshow/108366169.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108366169.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 08:25:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/polls-open-in-portugals-general-election-with-mainstream-moderates-trying-to-keep-populists-at-bay/articleshow/108366169.cms</guid></item><item><title>“这是一种生活方式”：女性在乌克兰军队中留下自己的印记</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/its-a-way-of-life-women-make-their-mark-in-the-ukrainian-army/articleshow/108364262.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108364262.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管面临挑战，随着与俄罗斯的战争继续，越来越多的乌克兰女性正在参军参战。目前正在努力解决军队内部基于性别的不平等和歧视问题。一些组织和倡议正在为女兵提供支持。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 06:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/its-a-way-of-life-women-make-their-mark-in-the-ukrainian-army/articleshow/108364262.cms</guid></item><item><title>俾路支省内阁将于两周内敲定：CM Sarfraz Bugti</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/balochistan-cabinet-to-be-finalised-within-two-weeks-cm-sarfraz-bugti/articleshow/108363826.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108363826.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俾路支省首席部长萨弗拉兹·布格蒂宣布，省内阁将在未来两周内敲定。阿西夫·阿里·扎尔达里的胜利、远见和对俾路支人民权利的承诺得到了强调。会上提到了有关俾路支省问题的持续对话。增加了萨弗拉兹·布格蒂 (Sarfraz Bugti) 的宣誓就职。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 06:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/balochistan-cabinet-to-be-finalised-within-two-weeks-cm-sarfraz-bugti/articleshow/108363826.cms</guid></item><item><title>中巴友谊是“历史的选择”：习近平迎接巴基斯坦新任总统扎尔达里</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-pak-friendship-choice-of-history-xi-jinping-greets-new-pak-president-zardari/articleshow/108363764.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108363764.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;习近平主席祝贺巴基斯坦总统扎尔达里当选，强调中巴两国铁杆友谊和战略意义。两国高层交往密切，中巴经济走廊建设取得丰硕成果。中国还提供外国贷款和债务展期来帮助巴基斯坦应对严重的经济危机。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 06:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-pak-friendship-choice-of-history-xi-jinping-greets-new-pak-president-zardari/articleshow/108363764.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国在重要政治会议期间加强对互联网的控制</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-tightens-grip-over-internet-during-key-political-meeting/articleshow/108362819.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108362819.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;本周，数千名代表齐聚北京，参加一年一度的“两会”会议，VPN 软件越来越难以规避审查，而中断也变得更加频繁，即使与之前的敏感政治事件相比也是如此。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 05:22:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-tightens-grip-over-internet-during-key-political-meeting/articleshow/108362819.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧盟在议会选举前面临虚假信息激增</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-faces-surge-of-disinformation-ahead-of-parliamentary-elections/articleshow/108361699.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108361699.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着议会选举的临近，欧盟正面临社交媒体上的虚假信息浪潮。诸如禁止汽车维修和在食品中隐藏昆虫成分等虚假主张已经疯传并被揭穿。欧盟最高外交官何塞普·博雷尔强调虚假信息是一个重大威胁。专家指出，对欧盟决策过程的无知导致了负面看法和不信任。打击虚假信息需要解决公民的融入问题并促进准确的信息。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 04:08:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-faces-surge-of-disinformation-ahead-of-parliamentary-elections/articleshow/108361699.cms</guid></item><item><title>海地暴力升级：数十人寻求庇护，联合国警告“城市被围困”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/haiti-violence-escalates-dozens-seek-refuge-un-warns-of-city-under-siege/articleshow/108361759.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108361759.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在海地首都帮派暴力激增之际，武装袭击者袭击了总统府和警察总部。犯罪派系意图推翻亨利总理，造成严重破坏，居民纷纷到公共建筑避难。超过 362,000 名海地人在国内流离失所。美国敦促政治改革，而海地面临人道主义危机。加共体召开紧急行动。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 04:25:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/haiti-violence-escalates-dozens-seek-refuge-un-warns-of-city-under-siege/articleshow/108361759.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：PML-N高级领导人伊沙克·达尔将成为新任财政部长</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-pml-n-senior-leader-ishaq-dar-to-become-the-new-finance-minister/articleshow/108361643.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108361643.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据 ARY News 援引消息人士报道，巴基斯坦穆斯林联盟纳瓦兹 (PML-N) 高级领导人伊沙克·达尔 (Ishaq Dar) 退出新任财政部长竞选。在与其兄弟纳瓦兹·谢里夫讨论后，巴基斯坦总理谢赫巴兹·谢里夫最终确定了联邦内阁成员。被认为与谢里夫家族关系密切的四任财政部长伊沙克·达尔将接任外交部长。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 04:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-pml-n-senior-leader-ishaq-dar-to-become-the-new-finance-minister/articleshow/108361643.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚山洪暴发和山体滑坡造成至少 21 人死亡、多人失踪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesia-flash-floods-and-landslide-reports-at-least-21-dead-and-several-missing/articleshow/108361171.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108361171.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据官方周日称，暴雨引发的山洪和山体滑坡已导致印度尼西亚苏门答腊岛至少 21 人丧生，据报道仍有 7 人失踪。​​​当地灾害管理机构负责人多尼·尤斯里扎尔 (Doni Yusrizal) 表示，截至周六，救援人员已在受灾最严重的 Koto XI Tarusan 村打捞出七具尸体。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 03:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesia-flash-floods-and-landslide-reports-at-least-21-dead-and-several-missing/articleshow/108361171.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>